  ["tips.deathknight.presence.master"] = "Specialisation Control|cffffffff\nAllows choosing, enabling, or disabling a Death Knight's specialisation.|r\n\n|cffff0000Left-click to show or hide Options|r\n|cff999999(Executed by: System)|r\n\n|cffff0000Right-click to toggle the default specialisation.|r\n|cff999999(Executed by: Bot)|r",
